visualiser_mayavi module¶

contains a UI to view all the pickle files present in the target folder of data/Segmentation_and_landmarks_processed. To view the meshes, simply .. code-block:: console

$ python3 visualiser_mayavi.py

and change the directory to the one containing the processed pickle files.
